772
00:46:05,063 --> 00:46:09,646
<i>As you may know, there was an attempt
on my life by a vigilante last night,</i>

773
00:46:10,438 --> 00:46:14,813
<i>and in the act of sabotage,
our city's power grid was disrupted.</i>

774
00:46:15,604 --> 00:46:20,021
<i>While facing rampant lawlessness,
Commissioner Gallo...</i>

775
00:46:22,229 --> 00:46:23,896
