776
00:46:27,229 --> 00:46:29,854
To turn his back
on the people of New York.

777
00:46:30,646 --> 00:46:32,438
The thin blue line has broken.

778
00:46:34,313 --> 00:46:38,021
[hesitates] I will not allow you
to live in fear, though.

779
00:46:38,729 --> 00:46:42,396
<i>I am enacting my Safer Streets initiative.</i>

780
00:46:43,271 --> 00:46:48,520
<i>Effective immediately,
all vigilante activity is illegal,</i>

781
00:46:48,521 --> 00:46:52,104
<i>and it will be dealt with accordingly.</i>

782
