Curfew is at 8:00 p.m.

783
00:46:55,396 --> 00:46:56,938
[sirens blaring]

784
00:46:58,813 --> 00:47:00,479
And in the immediate future,

785
00:47:02,813 --> 00:47:06,271
New York City is under martial law. Now...

786
00:47:07,854 --> 00:47:11,395
