Like a mask and a purpose
could save my life.

800
00:48:12,688 --> 00:48:13,688
Didn't it?

801
00:48:15,021 --> 00:48:16,063
No.

802
00:48:16,729 --> 00:48:18,188
It wasn't the mask.

803
00:48:20,646 --> 00:48:23,313
It wasn't me needing
to believe in it that saved me.

804
00:48:26,854 --> 00:48:29,688
My mistake was thinking
I was immune to the darkness.

805
00:48:32,979 --> 00:48:34,646
And I let it creep inside me.

806
00:48:37,104 --> 00:48:38,563
I let the dark power me.

807
00:48:39,521 --> 00:48:41,813
I threw Poindexter off that rooftop.

808
00:48:43,563 --> 00:48:46,604
- Karen, I wanted to kill him.
- [sighs]

809
