The truth is,

810
00:48:53,354 --> 00:48:54,729
ever since Foggy died...

811
00:48:58,271 --> 00:49:00,354
- I didn't know who I was anymore.
- [Karen sighs]

812
00:49:03,813 --> 00:49:06,938
[breathes deeply] Foggy believed in you.

813
00:49:07,813 --> 00:49:10,479
Whatever you wanna call yourself.
Whatever's...

814
00:49:11,271 --> 00:49:13,646
Behind the mask, behind your eyes...

815
