[breath trembling]

816
00:49:16,438 --> 00:49:19,438
...that's wrath, and that's mercy.

817
00:49:20,896 --> 00:49:24,604
That's the dark and the light.
He knew all of it. All of it.

818
00:49:25,688 --> 00:49:26,771
He knew you.

819
